WEBVTT

00:07.560 --> 00:08.920
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:40.240 --> 01:42.840
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:46.880 --> 01:49.240
I had calculated every move,

01:50.600 --> 01:53.120
yet the one I held dearest
threw it all into ruin.

01:53.720 --> 01:55.200
Had she not interfered,

01:55.280 --> 01:56.880
we'd never have endured such indignity.

01:58.720 --> 01:59.560
No.

02:01.000 --> 02:02.440
I should thank her

02:04.320 --> 02:06.320
for making one thing clear.

02:08.160 --> 02:10.000
Even the most masterful stratagem

02:10.840 --> 02:13.720
cannot withstand a sudden turn of fortune.

02:16.520 --> 02:18.800
Just like this game,

02:18.880 --> 02:20.880
I thought victory was all but assured,

02:20.960 --> 02:22.480
and yet I forgot

02:23.240 --> 02:24.400
that the opponent

02:25.320 --> 02:27.480
does not always play by your script.

02:29.560 --> 02:33.360
I had accounted for everyone, except her.

02:34.680 --> 02:36.440
Who would have thought

02:36.520 --> 02:39.920
that the little girl
who once wept in public

02:40.560 --> 02:45.200
would dare to take the pieces in hand
amid such chaos?

02:48.640 --> 02:51.440
But one such mistake

02:52.280 --> 02:53.640
is all it takes.

03:18.280 --> 03:21.160
Your Majesty, please accept the offering.

03:23.400 --> 03:27.160
The Divine Bird descends to the shrine

03:27.760 --> 03:31.680
as ancestral might protects the land.

03:32.520 --> 03:36.120
The divine aura soars
like swirling clouds,

03:37.280 --> 03:41.640
bestowing grace to nourish the realm.

03:53.920 --> 03:55.400
<i>Chu Zhao has put Deng Yi and Xie Yanfang</i>

03:55.480 --> 03:57.440
in charge of all ancestral rites,

03:57.520 --> 03:59.120
even the shamans' invocations included.

03:59.200 --> 04:01.040
Will this compromise our plan?

04:01.120 --> 04:02.280
Tomorrow,

04:02.360 --> 04:04.320
once the herbs are lit,

04:05.680 --> 04:07.600
Xiao Yu, standing nearest to the censer,

04:08.560 --> 04:09.840
will inhale

04:13.240 --> 04:14.560
the poisoned smoke.

04:15.600 --> 04:18.399
She will surely guard
against every possibility.

04:19.360 --> 04:20.360
Yet

04:21.320 --> 04:22.920
once the smoke rises,

04:24.880 --> 04:26.880
her days as Grand Princess

04:28.760 --> 04:30.200
are over.

04:32.200 --> 04:33.600
What's wrong?

04:34.680 --> 04:35.760
Yu.

04:37.400 --> 04:39.440
Yu.

04:39.520 --> 04:41.480
Yu. Yu!

04:41.560 --> 04:42.400
Are you alright?

04:42.480 --> 04:43.720
-Your Majesty. Your Majesty.
-Yu.

04:43.800 --> 04:45.040
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

04:45.120 --> 04:46.680
Wake up. Yu.

04:48.360 --> 04:52.280
Dark omens shadow the throne
as the Grand Princess's fate

04:52.360 --> 04:55.360
-Yu.
-collides with the Emperor's.

04:55.440 --> 04:57.320
-Wake up.
-It is as if the heavens

04:57.400 --> 04:59.560
-What happened to you?
-seek to sever the imperial lifeline!

05:00.160 --> 05:02.480
The Grand Princess has plotted
against His Majesty.

05:02.560 --> 05:03.600
Seize her at once!

05:07.960 --> 05:10.960
Whoever dares to touch Her Highness
answers to my blade.

05:11.040 --> 05:14.240
How insolent you are
to draw steel before His Majesty!

05:15.280 --> 05:16.560
None shall presume!

05:17.280 --> 05:20.120
Summon the Imperial Physician
to tend to His Majesty.

05:21.120 --> 05:22.160
Seal the palace gates.

05:22.240 --> 05:25.040
None shall leave without express command.

06:01.840 --> 06:04.280
Mr. Deng, please forgive me.

06:04.360 --> 06:07.040
His Majesty's pulse shows no irregularity.

06:07.120 --> 06:09.240
Then why does he remain unconscious?

06:09.320 --> 06:11.080
I cannot find the cause.

06:11.680 --> 06:12.720
But His Majesty's condition,

06:12.800 --> 06:15.480
falling unconscious
after inhaling the smoke,

06:15.560 --> 06:18.040
is strikingly similar
to the Crown Prince's poisoning.

06:18.120 --> 06:19.280
Have you identified the toxin?

06:19.360 --> 06:22.160
The Crown Prince's death
was never truly probed in time,

06:22.240 --> 06:23.920
so the source remains a mystery.

06:24.000 --> 06:25.960
-Keep digging.
-Yes.

06:29.840 --> 06:31.280
What should we do?

06:31.360 --> 06:35.880
Everyone involved in the poisoning
is right here.

06:38.000 --> 06:40.160
Why not ask them outright?

06:45.520 --> 06:46.400
How is His Majesty?

06:53.200 --> 06:54.560
What is the condition? I must go in.

06:54.640 --> 06:56.440
His Majesty is being attended to.

06:56.520 --> 06:57.800
No one is permitted to enter.

06:58.400 --> 06:59.160
Your Highness.

06:59.240 --> 07:03.160
By law, the implicated
must be held for questioning.

07:03.240 --> 07:05.320
Leaving your palace unbidden now

07:05.400 --> 07:08.400
will only make things harder to resolve.

07:09.280 --> 07:10.440
It wasn't me.

07:13.120 --> 07:14.280
What has become of Yu?

07:19.560 --> 07:21.160
He has yet to awaken.

07:21.240 --> 07:23.600
Acupuncture and herbs
have been administered.

07:26.160 --> 07:28.960
-What happened?
-Yet when His Majesty was poisoned,

07:29.920 --> 07:32.880
you were the only one by his side.

07:32.960 --> 07:34.000
Zhao.

07:38.400 --> 07:39.560
The Imperial Physician said

07:40.280 --> 07:43.880
his symptoms are identical
to those of his father.

07:45.120 --> 07:46.120
Mr. Xiao,

07:46.760 --> 07:48.840
do you know what poison His Majesty took?

07:52.880 --> 07:54.400
How strange you should ask.

07:55.360 --> 07:59.000
Given it was the Third Prince's doing,

07:59.080 --> 08:00.600
how should I know?

08:01.360 --> 08:03.520
The shaman

08:04.560 --> 08:06.240
has branded her a jinx.

08:06.320 --> 08:07.960
I was skeptical at first.

08:08.680 --> 08:10.200
But with His Majesty at death's door,

08:10.280 --> 08:12.600
rather than pursuing the true culprit,

08:12.680 --> 08:14.240
you stand here questioning me?

08:15.000 --> 08:18.040
Xiao Xun, I am the Grand Princess,

08:18.120 --> 08:19.960
-not some jinx you claimed.
-Very well.

08:21.080 --> 08:23.720
Perhaps you find me an eyesore

08:24.400 --> 08:26.160
and wish to pin the blame on me

08:26.240 --> 08:27.320
just to have me out of the way.

08:27.400 --> 08:28.880
Nonsense.

08:28.960 --> 08:31.160
Your Highness has quite the nerve,

08:31.240 --> 08:34.720
pinning this atrocity on me
without any proof.

08:34.799 --> 08:35.799
This is outrageous.

08:35.880 --> 08:37.080
Your Highness is the one

08:37.880 --> 08:39.960
who owes an answer for this.

08:40.039 --> 08:42.320
The shaman has divined an ill omen.

08:42.400 --> 08:44.680
Your Highness ought
not to remain here any longer.

08:46.960 --> 08:49.040
If Your Highness has nothing to hide,

08:49.120 --> 08:51.040
you might as well step aside

08:51.120 --> 08:52.760
and let the truth run its course.

08:53.640 --> 08:54.760
Indeed.

08:54.840 --> 08:56.600
-That's right.
-Yes.

08:57.480 --> 08:58.320
Enough.

08:58.400 --> 08:59.840
Everyone, calm yourselves.

09:00.440 --> 09:02.000
Something is amiss here.

09:02.520 --> 09:04.760
It concerns the stability of the realm.

09:05.280 --> 09:11.280
Please remain in your palace
until the truth comes to light.

09:12.800 --> 09:14.360
-Someone.
-I'll do it.

09:37.800 --> 09:41.040
His Majesty requires rest,

09:41.120 --> 09:43.280
and I shall not disturb further.

09:44.040 --> 09:45.200
I shall depart.

09:49.280 --> 09:50.200
We should leave too.

09:50.280 --> 09:51.760
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

09:51.840 --> 09:53.760
His Majesty needs rest.

09:53.840 --> 09:55.920
What a scene.

09:58.120 --> 10:00.080
You seem unbothered leaving your brother

10:02.920 --> 10:04.600
to keep watch over her.

10:04.680 --> 10:06.080
If you're worried,

10:07.240 --> 10:09.120
you can take his place.

10:12.280 --> 10:13.800
That's right. It has been a while.

10:13.880 --> 10:15.600
When will His Majesty wake?

10:28.520 --> 10:31.360
Jiu, stay here and keep watch.
I will go find Yu.

10:33.120 --> 10:35.960
Alright. I have already briefed
the guards at his door.

10:58.160 --> 11:01.280
Yu, wake up. It's alright.

11:05.280 --> 11:07.360
Zhao, how was my performance?

11:07.440 --> 11:08.800
I even fooled the Imperial Physician.

11:10.200 --> 11:11.760
Once you have had your pastries,

11:11.840 --> 11:14.160
the physician will report
that you have come to.

11:14.760 --> 11:16.440
You must keep it up a while longer.

11:18.520 --> 11:19.680
I'm sorry.

11:20.680 --> 11:21.760
Don't be.

11:21.840 --> 11:23.720
We are catching the villain together.

11:23.800 --> 11:25.240
I can play my part.

11:28.480 --> 11:30.160
But if something goes wrong,

11:33.080 --> 11:34.080
you could be in danger.

11:35.000 --> 11:38.160
You risked your life
to save me among the rebels.

11:38.240 --> 11:40.600
I trust you will keep me safe.

11:41.400 --> 11:42.720
Rest easy.

11:42.800 --> 11:46.320
It will not be long
before I catch the culprit.

11:46.400 --> 11:47.960
And once this is over,

11:48.040 --> 11:50.920
remember to build me a grand swing.

11:57.000 --> 11:58.960
I promise I will.

12:03.560 --> 12:04.640
Your Highness.

12:04.720 --> 12:05.960
What is it?

12:07.080 --> 12:09.480
Word has come His Majesty is awake.

12:11.840 --> 12:12.840
Impossible.

12:14.040 --> 12:16.600
Golden Finch Venom has no antidote.

12:16.680 --> 12:17.800
How could they have cured him?

12:17.880 --> 12:21.640
The Imperial Physician says
the two toxins are identical.

12:21.720 --> 12:23.080
That poison is ours alone.

12:23.160 --> 12:24.880
Is it possible they'd link it to us?

12:25.840 --> 12:28.080
There is no hard evidence.

12:28.160 --> 12:29.560
Do not lose your nerve.

12:30.280 --> 12:32.400
Go investigate.

12:33.480 --> 12:35.680
The Emperor's guards
have been replaced by Xie Yanlai

12:36.480 --> 12:37.560
and reinforced.

12:37.640 --> 12:39.760
Deng Yi has ordered
that no one is to visit.

12:43.040 --> 12:44.320
No one?

13:09.160 --> 13:10.840
As his uncle,

13:11.800 --> 13:13.600
I should call upon him.

13:28.200 --> 13:32.120
Concerned for His Majesty,
I've come to pay my respects.

13:33.760 --> 13:35.720
Please wait. Mr. Deng ordered

13:35.800 --> 13:39.040
that all visitors
must first go through him.

13:39.120 --> 13:43.600
His Majesty and I are of the same lineage.

13:43.680 --> 13:45.120
Does that count for nothing here?

13:45.200 --> 13:47.960
It is so grave
that we have to stay on guard.

13:48.560 --> 13:49.560
Please understand, Your Highness.

13:49.640 --> 13:52.840
Against the culprit or me?

13:52.920 --> 13:54.600
What is it

13:55.640 --> 13:57.560
that has displeased you so?

13:58.440 --> 13:59.640
Is the medicine ready?

14:05.880 --> 14:07.800
Don't be so rigid.

14:07.880 --> 14:10.280
He is only worried about His Majesty.

14:10.880 --> 14:12.040
Let him through.

14:12.120 --> 14:13.560
-But…
-What?

14:14.960 --> 14:18.720
My word is just as valid as Mr. Deng's.

14:22.040 --> 14:23.640
There is no need for such a temper.

14:24.400 --> 14:26.000
They are merely following orders.

14:27.080 --> 14:28.120
Please follow me.

14:43.520 --> 14:44.400
Your Majesty.

14:48.280 --> 14:50.040
It has been but a few days,

14:51.440 --> 14:53.480
-yet you've grown so frail.
-Your Highness,

14:54.640 --> 14:56.080
I am afraid this is not proper.

15:03.560 --> 15:05.920
The poison is indeed difficult to counter.

15:06.000 --> 15:08.760
Fortunately, His Majesty is blessed,

15:08.840 --> 15:10.640
and Her Highness has found the antidote.

15:12.360 --> 15:14.320
The remedy is complex, however,

15:15.120 --> 15:18.120
and must be taken for nine days
before it takes effect.

15:20.880 --> 15:24.280
Then give His Majesty
the medicine at once.

15:26.600 --> 15:27.640
By Mr. Deng's command,

15:27.720 --> 15:29.760
you two lords must depart immediately.

15:30.560 --> 15:31.520
Presumptuous.

15:40.080 --> 15:41.240
I'm here to call on His Majesty.

15:41.320 --> 15:43.000
Who is he to interfere?

16:00.640 --> 16:03.720
<i>How did you know</i>
<i>that the poison he used at the ritual</i>

16:04.520 --> 16:06.360
was the same one
that killed the Crown Prince?

16:06.440 --> 16:08.880
-I didn't.
-You didn't?

16:09.480 --> 16:12.240
Then why did you tell him Yu had awakened?

16:13.080 --> 16:14.600
I was baiting him.

16:15.280 --> 16:20.040
Moving against Yu proves
he killed the Crown Prince, too.

16:21.440 --> 16:22.400
You were using

16:23.760 --> 16:25.160
His Majesty as bait.

16:35.040 --> 16:36.400
That is why I needed you

16:37.120 --> 16:38.680
in the shadows.

16:39.200 --> 16:40.960
To catch him

16:42.600 --> 16:44.080
red-handed

16:44.680 --> 16:46.440
when the time comes.

16:51.200 --> 16:52.600
But what if he does not come?

16:55.400 --> 16:56.560
Your brother will help.

17:01.640 --> 17:05.359
He has seen my devotion to Yu.

17:07.000 --> 17:08.040
He will assist me.

17:14.839 --> 17:16.720
Why are you so set
on sending Xiao Xun to his grave?

17:16.800 --> 17:18.200
Because he deserves no less.

17:23.680 --> 17:27.079
-If you make a mistake--
-Then ensure no such thing happens.

17:50.960 --> 17:53.080
Xiao Xun, what do you think you are doing?

17:57.560 --> 17:58.920
Yu. Yu.

17:59.520 --> 18:00.480
Yu.

18:02.600 --> 18:03.440
Yu.

18:05.680 --> 18:07.400
Yu. Yu.

18:08.280 --> 18:09.120
Yu.

18:12.360 --> 18:13.200
Zhao.

18:14.280 --> 18:15.600
I am fine.

18:16.360 --> 18:17.760
I just fell asleep.

18:45.680 --> 18:47.720
Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,

18:47.800 --> 18:49.600
attempted to poison the Emperor.

18:49.680 --> 18:51.000
This crime is unforgivable.

18:54.880 --> 18:57.400
With nothing but bare words,

18:57.920 --> 19:00.560
Your Highness would charge me
with poisoning?

19:00.640 --> 19:01.760
What's your proof?

19:02.360 --> 19:04.040
Summon the Imperial Physician.
Test the medicine.

19:04.120 --> 19:05.760
Summon the Imperial Physician.

19:48.040 --> 19:52.680
Your Highness, Mr. Deng, it's non-toxic.

19:52.760 --> 19:53.920
Impossible.

19:54.000 --> 19:54.840
What…

19:54.920 --> 19:56.600
What's going on?

19:56.680 --> 20:00.120
-What on earth is going on?
-How?

20:00.200 --> 20:03.360
-But his Majesty is indeed poisoned.
-Right.

20:03.880 --> 20:04.800
Then who did it?

20:04.880 --> 20:06.640
I saw him do it.

20:20.000 --> 20:21.000
Zhao,

20:21.880 --> 20:25.320
your little trap

20:25.920 --> 20:27.640
was far too rushed.

20:27.720 --> 20:29.440
In that case,

20:29.520 --> 20:31.400
I'll prepare a gift for you.

20:32.000 --> 20:33.800
What? A trap?

20:33.880 --> 20:36.840
Golden Finch Venom has no antidote.

20:36.920 --> 20:40.400
And after the coup that day,

20:40.920 --> 20:42.640
no one ever examined

20:43.760 --> 20:45.640
the Crown Prince's body.

20:46.800 --> 20:47.800
So,

20:49.080 --> 20:52.200
the news must be false.

20:54.200 --> 20:57.520
Have the Imperial Physician
decant a calming draft

20:58.400 --> 20:59.760
into this vial.

21:05.600 --> 21:09.880
Your Highness is clearly
the prime suspect for the poisoning.

21:09.960 --> 21:13.040
Yet you're framing me

21:13.640 --> 21:15.880
for regicide.

21:16.480 --> 21:20.000
So, you must be certain
I tainted this tonic.

21:20.600 --> 21:22.080
And yet,

21:22.160 --> 21:25.160
you left me alone with His Majesty.

21:25.240 --> 21:27.640
What is your true intent?

21:27.720 --> 21:30.000
Have you no regard for His Majesty's life?

21:31.000 --> 21:32.960
-Exactly.
-Indeed.

21:33.760 --> 21:37.000
-It could have hurt his Majesty.
-Indeed.

21:37.080 --> 21:42.520
We shared a deep bond for many years.

21:43.880 --> 21:45.480
Even when our betrothal ended,

21:46.000 --> 21:50.280
I knew feelings cannot be swayed.

21:52.640 --> 21:54.920
Yet, to my dismay,

21:56.600 --> 21:57.440
you spurn

21:58.520 --> 22:03.360
our past and seek my very life.

22:04.120 --> 22:06.640
Whatever our grievances,

22:07.160 --> 22:10.840
you had no right to use His Majesty
as a bait to frame me.

22:10.920 --> 22:13.480
Such treachery is unforgivable.

22:14.080 --> 22:18.800
Your Highness,
how could you be so reckless?

22:19.400 --> 22:20.680
The Emperor's life is sacred,

22:20.760 --> 22:23.200
not a pawn for you to manipulate at will.

22:23.280 --> 22:26.160
Should any harm befall him,
even death could not atone for your guilt.

22:26.760 --> 22:27.880
Indeed.

22:27.960 --> 22:32.000
We cannot allow such a treacherous villain
to corrupt this court.

22:32.080 --> 22:35.160
Bearing a title of national honor,

22:35.240 --> 22:37.520
yet you are devious and ruthless.

22:37.600 --> 22:41.160
If this goes unpunished,
where is the sanctity of our laws?

22:41.240 --> 22:42.760
Where is the integrity of this court?

22:43.480 --> 22:47.000
And how can we face the late Emperor?

22:49.040 --> 22:51.440
Save your breath.

22:51.520 --> 22:53.600
The truth is plain as day to you.
Bring her in.

22:55.320 --> 22:57.840
DILIGENT AND VIRTUOUS

23:15.440 --> 23:18.120
No wonder Yu's been haunted
in dreams lately.

23:18.200 --> 23:20.280
Turns out someone's been playing tricks.

23:30.880 --> 23:31.720
Your Majesty.

23:31.800 --> 23:33.240
-Zhao!
-Your Majesty. What's the matter?

23:33.320 --> 23:34.480
-Zhao!
-Your Majesty.

23:35.040 --> 23:35.920
Your Majesty.

23:37.120 --> 23:38.320
Yu.

23:38.400 --> 23:39.880
Yu. Come here.

23:40.600 --> 23:41.560
What's wrong?

23:42.080 --> 23:43.320
What happened?

23:43.400 --> 23:45.960
Your Highness, His Majesty has been waking
from nightmares for nights.

23:46.040 --> 23:48.040
Even the calming soup is all in vain.

23:49.360 --> 23:51.280
Zhao, I'm scared.

24:01.240 --> 24:02.480
It's no nightmare.

24:05.440 --> 24:07.160
Any new dishes on his table lately?

24:07.240 --> 24:09.600
Or any new ornaments placed here?

24:09.680 --> 24:10.560
The food is the same.

24:10.640 --> 24:12.720
But many tributes
and new pieces have been brought in.

24:12.800 --> 24:14.160
-Check them.
-Yes.

24:20.960 --> 24:22.200
There, there.

24:22.280 --> 24:23.920
I'm here.

24:26.680 --> 24:29.440
I saw candles flickering within,
shadows rushing about.

24:29.520 --> 24:30.880
What has happened?

24:30.960 --> 24:33.640
The air reeks of foul play.

24:44.240 --> 24:45.760
This incense…

24:53.760 --> 24:54.600
Let me.

25:10.480 --> 25:12.160
Calming incense

25:13.120 --> 25:14.200
should be fine as dust,

25:14.800 --> 25:15.760
completely pure.

25:16.680 --> 25:20.880
Yet this is laced with grit.

25:20.960 --> 25:24.280
It seems someone
is trying to poison the air.

25:25.160 --> 25:27.600
The toxins vanish with the smoke,

25:27.680 --> 25:29.280
destroying the evidence as it burns.

25:30.440 --> 25:34.960
This is the same way that killed
the Crown Prince.

25:36.720 --> 25:37.800
-Xiao Xun.
-Xiao Xun.

25:40.480 --> 25:42.400
We should find the traitor now.

25:45.080 --> 25:45.920
No.

25:47.200 --> 25:48.720
Don't alert them.

25:50.680 --> 25:54.600
To think he could reach Yu so easily.

25:54.680 --> 25:55.840
The mole will be hard to find.

25:58.280 --> 26:00.480
Yu, I have an idea.

26:01.240 --> 26:03.120
Since they're disturbing your dreams,

26:03.200 --> 26:06.200
let's play along and draw them out.

26:06.280 --> 26:07.120
Scared?

26:07.200 --> 26:09.880
Not with you two here.

26:11.000 --> 26:12.600
Replace the incense.

26:12.680 --> 26:14.680
The Chenxiang incense was too strong.

26:14.760 --> 26:17.760
Change it to a blend
with Fuling and Yuanzhi.

26:18.360 --> 26:19.480
At once, Your Highness.

26:20.840 --> 26:23.760
<i>I've replaced the incense</i>
<i>with Golden Finch Venom.</i>

26:24.280 --> 26:27.800
<i>I knew you wouldn't leave this matter be.</i>

26:29.800 --> 26:32.840
<i>So, you proposed the sacrifice</i>
<i>in court again.</i>

26:32.920 --> 26:35.600
I have something to report.

26:35.680 --> 26:39.440
<i>You were certain</i>
<i>Yu would mention the nightmares.</i>

26:40.040 --> 26:41.240
<i>So I played along</i>

26:42.440 --> 26:44.760
<i>with your little show at the ritual,</i>

26:46.120 --> 26:47.560
<i>to lure you into it.</i>

26:53.720 --> 26:55.480
You poisoned the Chenxiang incense too,

26:55.560 --> 26:57.320
didn't you?

26:58.600 --> 27:00.960
Who is the mastermind behind this?

27:01.040 --> 27:02.640
His Highness

27:03.600 --> 27:06.200
ordered me to dispose of the ash.

27:06.280 --> 27:08.280
I truly know nothing.

27:09.960 --> 27:11.120
Do you think the ash

27:11.200 --> 27:13.240
and a maid's testimony

27:14.000 --> 27:15.960
is enough to pin this on me?

27:16.560 --> 27:17.600
Proof?

27:19.200 --> 27:20.720
Without it,

27:20.800 --> 27:25.760
I could also say
she was coerced into slandering me.

27:43.600 --> 27:46.200
Does this face look familiar?

27:46.280 --> 27:48.000
He's from the Office
of the Great Supplicator.

27:49.160 --> 27:50.680
Before the ritual,

27:51.280 --> 27:55.600
I found that the attendant
preparing the herb wreath

27:56.120 --> 27:57.400
was an impostor.

27:58.120 --> 28:01.920
I intercepted him just in time and found

28:02.680 --> 28:04.360
a few trinkets on him.

28:27.160 --> 28:28.480
Who sent you?

28:32.800 --> 28:35.560
Speak. Who is your master?

28:40.720 --> 28:42.080
Talk.

28:43.520 --> 28:45.200
Who ordered this?

28:48.080 --> 28:49.440
Zhao, watch out!

28:56.040 --> 28:57.120
-Yanlai!
-Your Highness!

28:57.200 --> 28:58.840
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness!

29:03.720 --> 29:04.960
What?

29:31.400 --> 29:32.320
What?

29:32.400 --> 29:34.880
Drawing a blade before the throne.
Insolent fool.

29:37.120 --> 29:38.520
Did you order this?

29:44.400 --> 29:45.680
Overstepping?

29:46.560 --> 29:47.760
Giving orders and drawing swords

29:49.080 --> 29:50.080
instead of His Majesty?

29:50.160 --> 29:53.520
Killing in the court? What? Am I next?

29:54.440 --> 29:57.200
You're eyeing the Crown, aren't you?

29:57.280 --> 29:58.720
Please hold your tongue.

29:58.800 --> 30:02.480
That attendant was killed on the spot.

30:03.320 --> 30:04.840
Dead men tell no tales.

30:04.920 --> 30:09.160
You all claim he was the one
who poisoned the herbs,

30:09.840 --> 30:11.760
yet His Majesty is clearly unharmed.

30:11.840 --> 30:12.840
Very well.

30:13.480 --> 30:14.840
If so,

30:14.920 --> 30:18.920
then why did His Majesty
feign poisoning at the ritual

30:19.000 --> 30:20.840
and cause the officials to worry in vain?

30:22.640 --> 30:23.920
This is outrageous.

30:24.520 --> 30:27.640
His Majesty has been played
by a mere woman.

30:28.240 --> 30:30.240
What becomes of our nation's dignity?

30:30.320 --> 30:34.080
From the coronation
to ruling from behind the curtain,

30:34.160 --> 30:37.840
her ambitions to seize the throne
could not be clearer.

30:37.920 --> 30:41.840
-Chu Zhao's treason demands her death.
-Chu Zhao's treason demands her death.

30:41.920 --> 30:45.600
-Chu Zhao's treason demands her death.
-Chu Zhao's treason demands her death.

30:45.680 --> 30:48.000
Chu Zhao's treason…

30:48.080 --> 30:49.040
Silence!

30:51.480 --> 30:53.880
The Grand Princess has only ever sought
to ease my burdens.

30:53.960 --> 30:56.760
To say she has given her all
would be an understatement.

30:57.440 --> 30:59.680
To claim she manipulates me
from the shadows

31:00.280 --> 31:01.520
is sheer nonsense.

31:03.040 --> 31:05.840
From the day my incense
was first tampered with,

31:06.440 --> 31:11.360
I knew there was a traitor
plotting against me.

31:12.160 --> 31:14.280
Feigning the poisoning was my own idea.

31:15.160 --> 31:17.240
She only acted on my orders

31:17.320 --> 31:19.000
and has done nothing wrong.

31:19.080 --> 31:20.840
If any of you have objections,

31:20.920 --> 31:22.920
lay them before me.

31:23.000 --> 31:24.200
Do not trouble her.

31:24.720 --> 31:28.400
Your Majesty, you are still young,
unaware of the world's cruelty.

31:28.480 --> 31:31.600
I know who wishes me well.

31:31.680 --> 31:33.440
Given our blood ties,

31:33.520 --> 31:35.520
Uncle, for the days to come,

31:35.600 --> 31:37.600
rest at your estate.

31:37.680 --> 31:38.680
No court for now.

31:49.840 --> 31:52.120
Yes, Your Majesty.

31:54.000 --> 31:55.440
Hear my command.

31:55.960 --> 31:59.280
Anyone else plotting treason

31:59.360 --> 32:00.880
shall be executed!

32:04.240 --> 32:06.920
Mr. Deng, Mr. Xie, do you concur?

32:08.080 --> 32:09.480
Your Majesty is wise.

32:09.560 --> 32:12.880
We abide by your will.

32:13.480 --> 32:16.160
-Your Majesty is wise.
-Your Majesty is wise.

32:16.240 --> 32:18.800
Alright. That concludes today's matter.

32:19.320 --> 32:21.320
Uncle, you may leave.

33:08.760 --> 33:10.880
Do you find me ridiculous as well?

33:14.960 --> 33:16.280
You grew up in the desert,

33:17.640 --> 33:18.640
so you must know

33:20.240 --> 33:22.160
the first time a wolf tears into its prey,

33:23.360 --> 33:24.680
it chokes on the stench of blood.

33:27.280 --> 33:28.360
But it

33:29.440 --> 33:31.440
never lets its prey
see the tremble of its own.

33:32.640 --> 33:33.720
Thank you

33:35.360 --> 33:36.720
for saving me.

33:40.200 --> 33:42.720
It was you who saved me.

33:44.640 --> 33:45.680
Don't pick up

33:46.760 --> 33:48.000
a blade ever again.

33:49.760 --> 33:50.800
Let me.

34:09.120 --> 34:09.960
No.

34:16.760 --> 34:17.600
No.

34:20.560 --> 34:21.800
If you don't want

34:23.920 --> 34:26.000
to end up dead,

34:28.040 --> 34:30.120
you must strike first.

34:42.239 --> 34:43.239
I told you

34:44.480 --> 34:46.239
I only did it

34:49.320 --> 34:51.480
to survive.

35:03.120 --> 35:08.080
<i>I fight so that more people may live!</i>

35:09.200 --> 35:11.120
What does Article Three
of the regulations say?

35:13.480 --> 35:14.680
Suspects

35:15.680 --> 35:17.120
must be handed over to the court-martial.

35:17.200 --> 35:19.120
Why did you attack him?

35:19.920 --> 35:22.360
He snuck into your tent.

35:22.440 --> 35:23.880
He has to be a spy.

35:23.960 --> 35:25.280
The Army Physician told me

35:26.040 --> 35:28.720
he came to beg for medicine
for his sick child.

35:28.800 --> 35:31.320
Do you know you nearly killed
an innocent soul?

35:35.720 --> 35:37.480
In such tumultuous times,

35:38.040 --> 35:39.960
innocence is but a cloak we wear.

35:41.040 --> 35:43.600
General, your military achievements

35:43.680 --> 35:45.520
and the path you tread

35:46.280 --> 35:48.280
are built upon the bodies
of these "innocents".

35:48.800 --> 35:51.640
We both waded through rivers of blood.

35:52.400 --> 35:53.840
Please spare me your talk of mercy.

35:58.480 --> 36:01.400
Have you seen this ravaged world

36:01.480 --> 36:03.800
and the lives struggling
through the fires of war?

36:04.440 --> 36:06.000
Every campaign I fought

36:07.320 --> 36:09.440
was to safeguard
the hearths and homes of this land.

36:09.520 --> 36:12.400
But if I kill the innocent
out of mere suspicion,

36:12.480 --> 36:15.600
then everything I've sacrificed to protect
loses all meaning.

36:18.400 --> 36:20.440
He's merely a father,
desperate to save his daughter,

36:20.520 --> 36:22.560
who nearly died at your hand.

36:22.640 --> 36:23.960
Tell me.

36:24.640 --> 36:25.840
Is he innocent or not?

36:27.280 --> 36:28.320
Remember.

36:29.080 --> 36:30.400
Amidst this chaos,

36:30.920 --> 36:32.440
our hearts must hold firm.

36:33.040 --> 36:37.320
I wage war so that more may live!

36:52.000 --> 36:54.120
What was on your mind?

36:55.320 --> 36:56.240
I just found out

36:59.800 --> 37:01.360
you're just like your father.

37:05.240 --> 37:06.080
So dull.

37:09.720 --> 37:10.760
Look who's talking.

37:14.720 --> 37:15.560
Fine.

37:16.760 --> 37:18.120
Bore as he is,

37:19.240 --> 37:21.480
his record on the battlefield
is legendary.

37:23.440 --> 37:26.800
Unlike someone
who can barely hold a sword steady.

37:27.960 --> 37:31.720
My father taught me horseback archery
and swordsmanship himself.

37:32.640 --> 37:34.200
He must've been a terrible instructor.

37:40.400 --> 37:42.800
I had my mind set on the Capital

37:46.080 --> 37:47.400
and never truly applied myself.

37:59.080 --> 38:00.160
Let me show you.

38:04.640 --> 38:05.720
Ready to learn?

39:35.600 --> 39:36.720
Why are you sweating so much?

39:51.880 --> 39:52.840
Nice work.

39:54.480 --> 39:56.160
I learned from the best, after all.

40:05.560 --> 40:07.680
Your Highness. You should get some rest.

40:27.600 --> 40:30.160
Put this on, lest you catch a cold.

40:31.920 --> 40:34.480
Is this cloak so repulsive to you?

43:24.480 --> 43:28.400
